## Module Status

### Object Explorer Architecture

Status: In progress.

Completed:
- Canonical admin URLs for core PeopleSoft objects:
  - `/admin/object/operator/{name}`
  - `/admin/object/role/{name}`
  - `/admin/object/permissionlist/{name}`
  - `/admin/object/component/{name}`
  - `/admin/object/page/{name}`
  - `/admin/object/record/{name}`
- Reusable object payload API at `/api/peoplesoft/object/{object_type}/{object_name}`
- Global search API at `/api/peoplesoft/search`
- `/admin/object` search landing page
- Reusable object page renderer with overview, actions, and sections
- Admin links added to graph/object relationship payloads
- Graph UI nodes navigate to canonical object pages

Remaining:
- Dedicated section renderers for PeopleCode, SQL, live usage, environment compare, reports
- More object types: menu, field, query, Application Engine, service operation, message, node, portal registry, content reference
- Full universal search coverage across all object types
- Breadcrumbs and recent objects
- Stronger visual hierarchy for large object pages

