### PeopleTools Metadata Engine

Status: Foundation complete.

Completed:
- `connectors/ptmetadata.py` — TTL-cached discovery connector
- Shared warning model
- Oracle/PeopleTools/schema version discovery
- `has_table()`, `has_column()`, `has_view()` capability helpers
- OBJECT_REGISTRY with discovery + search providers per object type
- Version adapter registry (8.58–8.62)
- Generic object resolver
- Provider-based universal search model
- `/api/peoplesoft/search` consumes provider model
- Metadata diagnostics APIs under `/api/metadata`
- `/admin/metadata` diagnostics UI

Remaining:
- Migrate existing object relationships to consume metadata relationship providers
- Implement concrete shared relationship providers (parents, children, references, security, pages, components, records, peoplecode, menus, portal)
- Add PeopleTools-version-specific adapters where table structures differ
- Expand OBJECT_REGISTRY search providers to Application Engine, IB, Query, Tree, CI, Portal

